## isEmpty variable

是否为空  "" \| null \| undefined \| Object.keys(target).length === 0 会返回 true， map \| set \| weakMap \| weakSet 判断 size === 0 时返回 true

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
isEmpty: (target: any) => any
```
